relation: Defines the conditions for redistributing routes from one routing protocol into another.
Replicates routes from another topology and another VRF.

Usage Guidelines Use this command to limit debug output to a single VRF. Note Enhanced Interior Gateway Routing Protocol (EIGRP) does not support the debug condition vrf command.
